-Then you say one.
-I wish

586
00:36:51,800 --> 00:36:53,000
we could share

587
00:36:54,220 --> 00:36:55,620
joy together every year.

588
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:14,320
That person

589
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:16,970
might not be me.

590
00:37:18,160 --> 00:37:20,160
I knew something was wrong with you.

591
00:37:21,680 --> 00:37:22,740
I want to resign.

592
00:37:23,450 --> 00:37:24,330
Hear me out.

593
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:27,060
First, it's for the greater good.

594
00:37:27,060 --> 00:37:28,660
As long as I stay in the court,

595
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:30,320
I'll always be a potential problem to you.

596
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:30,920
I appointed you

597
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:33,050
as the prime minister against all odds

598
00:37:33,480 --> 00:37:34,480
because I don't care

599
00:37:34,480 --> 00:37:35,880
about others' opinions.

600
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:38,860
We've been through so much together.

601
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:40,480
You will always be my

602
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:43,040
closest friend and the one I trust most.

603
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:47,240
Second,

604
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:49,680
it's also for myself.

605
00:38:10,720 --> 00:38:12,580
You're still thinking about her?

606
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:20,450
Jingguan asked me repeatedly in tears

607
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:23,130
why I wouldn't help her.

608
00:38:24,720 --> 00:38:25,680
But I kept clinging to

609
00:38:25,680 --> 00:38:27,140
what I believed was right.

610
00:38:29,460 --> 00:38:30,400
Yue Chi,

611
00:38:31,590 --> 00:38:32,800
it was not your fault.

612
00:38:33,830 --> 00:38:34,920
But she's dead,

613
00:38:36,680 --> 00:38:37,750
and I'm alive.

614
00:38:49,830 --> 00:38:51,890
Consider this a vacation for myself.

615
00:39:10,530 --> 00:39:11,800
Will we meet again?

616
00:39:17,640 --> 00:39:18,900
We will, Huo Jingheng.

617
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:20,920
We'll meet again.

618
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:34,070
One more time.

619
00:40:01,240 --> 00:40:02,160
This is...

620
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:03,760
Ms. Xue asked someone

621
00:40:03,760 --> 00:40:05,000
to give it to me

622
00:40:05,080 --> 00:40:06,240
for safekeeping.

623
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:07,480
She said if someone came

624
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:08,780
to pay respects to the late empress,

625
00:40:08,780 --> 00:40:10,180
I should give this to him.

626
00:40:13,600 --> 00:40:14,640
I'm sorry.

627
00:40:14,840 --> 00:40:15,720
Yue Chi.

628
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:17,280
Fate has given me

629
00:40:17,280 --> 00:40:18,600
gifts I don't deserve.

630
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:20,560
I can only accept one.

631
00:40:22,960 --> 00:40:25,840
Don't choose me in the next life.

632
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:32,810
At that moment in that year,

633
00:40:33,080 --> 00:40:35,100
if only I were the one

634
00:40:35,320 --> 00:40:36,980
who helped you up.

635
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:52,680
Your Grace!

636
00:40:52,680 --> 00:40:53,880
Slow down!

637
00:40:55,480 --> 00:40:56,560
Your Grace!

638
00:40:57,080 --> 00:40:58,280
Slow down!

639
00:41:03,210 --> 00:41:04,330
I adore you.

640
00:41:05,330 --> 00:41:06,290
I like you.

641
00:41:07,170 --> 00:41:08,040
I want you

642
00:41:08,130 --> 00:41:09,460
to stay, not just today.

643
00:41:09,970 --> 00:41:11,170
Every day from now on,

644
00:41:11,290 --> 00:41:11,930
I hope

645
00:41:11,930 --> 00:41:13,290
you can stay by my side,

646
00:41:14,010 --> 00:41:15,850
helping me and accompanying me,

647
00:41:16,770 --> 00:41:18,290
the emperor

648
00:41:19,450 --> 00:41:20,520
and also the man

649
00:41:20,550 --> 00:41:21,820
in front of you.

650
00:41:27,890 --> 00:41:28,450
Ling'er,

651
00:41:30,450 --> 00:41:31,930
are you willing?
